---
title: Cal Smart Honey-Thyme Chicken Breasts with Roasted Potatoes and Brussels Sprouts
description: This calorie smart supper is full of flavour, without the richness! Honey and thyme make a delicious glaze for tender chicken. Easy roasted potatoes and Brussels sprouts complete this ideal weeknight plate.

